    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，起点是Retail_Inventory。那接下来是直接从库存跳到优惠券系统，还是中间需要经过一个处理环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "中间应该还有一个库存相关的节点，我暂时也叫它Retail_Inventory，表示实际库存状态的确认环节。然后再连到Retail_CouponSystem，也就是优惠券发放系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我画一下：起点A是Retail_Inventory，连到B也是Retail_Inventory，再连到C是Retail_CouponSystem。方向都是从左到右。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
